# Airbnb Price Prediction (Flask Application)

This project is a Flask web application that predicts Airbnb listing prices based on host and property features.  
Instead of returning a single predicted price, the app provides a **dynamic price range** (prediction ± margin), giving hosts a more realistic view of market variability and model uncertainty.

---

## Features
- Flask backend serving predictions
- Frontend form (`index.html`) for user input
- Dynamic price range output (e.g., $100 → $80–$120)
- JSON API response for integration
- Clean project structure with `templates/` folder

---

## Project Structure
AirBnB-Flask-Application/
│
├── app.py                # Flask backend
├── final_model.pkl       # Trained Random Forest model
├── templates/
│   └── index.html        # Frontend form
└── README.md             # Project documentation
